<section id="register" class="tab-section">
<div class="container-registration rounded mt-2" style="background-image: url('https://8hxvw8tw.media.zestyio.com/COMM26-Red-White-Opaque-Background.png'); background-size: cover; background-position: center; background-repeat: no-repeat;">
<div class="middle-column-registration">
<p><img src="https://8hxvw8tw.media.zestyio.com/Loving-Like-Jesus-Commissioning-2026-Logo.png?width=327" alt="Loving-Like-Jesus-Commissioning-2026-Logo.png" width="327" style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;"></p>
<h4 style="text-align: center; display: none;">Register</h4>
<h4 style="text-align: center;" class="pt-4">Celebrate God’s Work. Honor Service. Be Inspired.</h4>
<p style="text-align: center;">Join us for Commissioning Weekend as we celebrate God’s call on the lives of new leaders in The Salvation Army. Together, we’ll honor faithful service, welcome newly commissioned officers, and recognize the volunteers and congregations whose support has made this journey possible. Experience vibrant worship, uplifting messages, and meaningful connection—celebrating faith, shared life, and the joy of serving God in community.</p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><strong>Location</strong>: Atlanta Temple, <a href="https://maps.app.goo.gl/mcJYvwAYsiAVLy2M8" target="_blank" rel="noopener">2090 N. Druid Hills Rd. N.E., Brookhaven, GA, 30329</a></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><strong>Date</strong>: June 5 – June 7, 2026</p>
<p style="text-align: center;">✅ Reserve your seat today!</p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://salarmy.us/registration-uss-commissioning-2026" target="_blank" class="btn btn-lg btn-primary mt-3 mb-5" rel="noopener">Register Here</a></p>
</div>
</div>
</section>
