<h4 style="text-align: center;">Special Guests</h4>
<div class="guests-grid"><!-- Captain Shinyoung Kang -->
<div class="guest-card"><img src="https://8hxvw8tw.media.zestyio.com/Shinyoung-Kang-Square.jpg" alt="Captain Shinyoung Kang" class="guest-photo">
<div class="guest-info">
<h5>Captain Shinyoung Kang</h5>
<p>Captain Shinyoung Kang is a dedicated Salvation Army officer of <a href="https://salvationarmyhouston.org/houston/international" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Houston International Corps</a>. She is known for her passionate leadership and commitment to community service. She has served in various capacities, inspiring others through her faith, compassion, and innovative ministry. Her work has impacted many lives, and she continues to be a role model in her field.</p>
<button class="btn btn-outline-primary mt-2 view-more-btn" data-guest="kang">View More</button></div>
</div>
<!-- Matt Ayars -->
<div class="guest-card"><img src="https://8hxvw8tw.media.zestyio.com/Matt-Ayars-Headshot-Square.jpeg" alt="Matt Ayars" class="guest-photo">
<div class="guest-info">
<h5>Matt Ayars</h5>
<p>Matt Ayars is the Lead Pastor of <a href="https://wellspringms.church" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Wellspring Church</a>. He previously served as President of Wesley Biblical Seminary and Emmaus University of Haiti, and is the author of several books. Matt earned a BA from Asbury University, an MA in Biblical Literature from Wesley Biblical Seminary, and a PhD in Old Testament Studies from the University of Chester.</p>
<button class="btn btn-outline-primary mt-2 view-more-btn" data-guest="ayers">View More</button></div>
</div>
<!-- Walter Kim -->
<div class="guest-card"><img src="https://8hxvw8tw.media.zestyio.com/WalterKim-Headshots-15.JPG" alt="Walter Kim" class="guest-photo">
<div class="guest-info">
<h5>Walter Kim</h5>
<p>Walter Kim is President of the <a href="http://nae.org/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">National Association of Evangelicals</a>. He earned his PhD at Harvard, was a chaplain at Yale, and has served in diverse pastoral ministries. He is on the board of World Relief, Christianity Today, and The Salvation Army, USA. He is often sought out for his theological and cultural commentary on issues facing the church and society.</p>
<button class="btn btn-outline-primary mt-2 view-more-btn" data-guest="kim">View More</button></div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
