<section id="youngadults" class="tab-section">
<div class="container-registration rounded mt-2" style="background-image: url('https://8hxvw8tw.media.zestyio.com/COMM26-Red-White-Opaque-Background.png'); background-size: cover; background-position: center; background-repeat: no-repeat;">
<div class="middle-column-registration">
<p><img src="https://8hxvw8tw.media.zestyio.com/Loving-Like-Jesus-Commissioning-2026-Logo.png?width=327" alt="Loving-Like-Jesus-Commissioning-2026-Logo.png" width="327" style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;"></p>
<h4 style="text-align: center;">Young Adults</h4>
<!-- <div class="youtube-video-container mb-4"><iframe width="560" height="315"
            src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/z3cXNUCrgaU?si=4pd830L4g0x5S5vN" title="YouTube video player"
            frameborder="0"
            allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share"
            referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen="allowfullscreen"></iframe></div>
            -->
<p style="text-align: center;"><strong>This Is Your Moment.</strong></p>
<p style="text-align: center;">At <strong>Commissioning 2026</strong>, you’re invited to be part of a powerful weekend of worship, connection, and purpose—with <strong>Saturday featuring special experiences for young adults</strong>. From community outreach and shared meals to passionate worship and send-offs for this year’s Summer Service Corps teams, it’s a day that puts your generation in the spotlight.</p>
<p style="text-align: center;">While the whole weekend brings us together, <strong>Saturday is a time to connect with others in your season of life</strong>, ask big questions, and lean into what God might be saying to you right now.</p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><strong>Pastors, mentors, leaders—encourage the young adults in your circles to show up.</strong><br>This isn’t a side track or a youth event. It’s a meaningful invitation to step fully into the life of the Church and the mission we share.</p>
<p style="text-align: center;">Don’t sit this one out.<br><strong>Come be part of something bigger at Commissioning 2026.</strong></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://salarmy.us/registration-uss-commissioning-2026" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="btn btn-lg btn-light my-3">Register Now</a></p>
</div>
</div>
</section>
<section id="youth" class="tab-section">
<div class="container-registration rounded mt-2" style="background-image: url('https://8hxvw8tw.media.zestyio.com/COMM26-Red-White-Opaque-Background.png'); background-size: cover; background-position: center; background-repeat: no-repeat;">
<div class="middle-column-registration">
<p><img src="https://8hxvw8tw.media.zestyio.com/Loving-Like-Jesus-Commissioning-2026-Logo.png?width=327" alt="Loving-Like-Jesus-Commissioning-2026-Logo.png" width="327" style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;"></p>
<p><img src="https://s3.amazonaws.com/uss-cache.salvationarmy.org/a519d42a-bb90-40df-8e12-f7c3d1b23a5d_Youth-Conference-at-Commissioning-2025-Logo.png" style="width: 314px; display: none; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;"></p>
<h4 style="text-align: center;">Youth Conference</h4>
<p style="text-align: center;">At Commissioning 2026, the Youth Conference offers an exciting, Christ-centered experience tailored for children ages 5–12, with loving and secure childcare available for little ones aged 6 months to 4 years. While you engage in powerful worship and teaching, your kids will be growing in their own faith through age-appropriate activities, dynamic Bible lessons, music, and new friendships in a safe, nurturing environment.</p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><strong>Parents and pastors</strong>—this is more than childcare. It’s an investment in the next generation of disciples.</p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><strong>Spots are limited!</strong> Pre-registration and completed paperwork are <strong>REQUIRED </strong>by <strong>Friday, May 29th</strong>—no exceptions.</span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;">Don’t miss this opportunity for your children to be part of something unforgettable.<br><!--Register now and let their faith journey grow alongside yours at Commissioning 2026!--></p>
<!-- <p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://salarmy.us/registration-uss-commissioning-2026" target="" class="btn btn-lg btn-light my-3">Sign Up Today</a></p> --></div>
</div>
</section>
<section id="lodging" class="tab-section">
<div class="container-registration rounded mt-2" style="background-image: url('https://8hxvw8tw.media.zestyio.com/COMM26-Red-White-Opaque-Background.png'); background-size: cover; background-position: center; background-repeat: no-repeat;">
<div class="middle-column-registration">
<p><img src="https://8hxvw8tw.media.zestyio.com/Loving-Like-Jesus-Commissioning-2026-Logo.png?width=327" alt="Loving-Like-Jesus-Commissioning-2026-Logo.png" width="327" style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;"></p>
<h4 style="text-align: center;">Lodging Information</h4>
<p style="text-align: center;">All General Attendees are welcome to book their own hotel rooms at a discounted rate at the following hotel. If you are booking for someone else, please ensure the reservation(s) are made in the name of the individual(s) staying in the room.<br><br><span style="font-size: 18px;"><strong>Marriott Courtyard</strong><br>1236 Executive Park Dr NE<br>Atlanta, GA 30329</span><br><br>To book, please click the "lodging details" button OR feel free to call the hotel directly at 888-236-2427;<br>and use the group name "Salvation Army Southern Territorial Headquarters Commissioning Event" to receive our special group rate!</p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><strong>GROUP RATE DEADLINE:</strong><br>Thursday, June 4, 2026</p>
<p style="text-align: center;">Please note that our event's hotel room block booking period may fill quickly. We recommend booking early to secure your accommodations. We look forward to welcoming you to Commissioning Weekend.</p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://www.marriott.com/event-reservations/reservation-link.mi?id=1727367293186&amp;key=GRP&amp;guestreslink2=true" target="_blank" class="btn btn-lg btn-light my-3" rel="noopener">Lodging Details</a></p>
</div>
